        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature that's frightened targets you with an attack.</p><hr /><p>You make a sudden threat toward a creature about to attack you that makes them flinch, throwing off their aim. You gain a +4 circumstance bonus to AC against the triggering attack. This reaction can't be triggered by the same creature again for 1 day.</p><hr /><p><strong>Special</strong> If you have @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Intimidating Glare], when you use this feat, you can have it lose the auditory trait and gain the visual trait.</p>"
